<p><a name="Quotes" id="Quotes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Toshio_Iwai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Quotes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Quotes</span></h2>
<p>"I've been longing for the feeling of my childhood in the digital world and that is why I've been sticking to relations among media, machine(s), and people through interactive works."<sup id="cite_ref-mmcagrandprixprofile_0-10" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-mmcagrandprixprofile-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p>"All of his work is sincere, and all consists of equal doses of seriousness and play, pathos and humor, intricacy and simplicity." - Azby Brown<sup id="cite_ref-wiredarticle_10-7" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-wiredarticle-10" title=""><span>[</span>11<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p><a name="Notable_works" id="Notable_works"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Toshio_Iwai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Notable works">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notable works</span></h2>
