<p><a name="Trivia" id="Trivia"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Toshio_Iwai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Trivia">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Trivia</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><i>Ugo Ugo Lhuga</i> is 'go-go girls' anagrammed in Japanese.<sup id="cite_ref-wiredarticle_10-8" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-wiredarticle-10" title=""><span>[</span>11<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
